## Coding Rules
- Always: Tailwind for all styling — no inline style objects except dynamic hex colors
- Always: IBM Plex Sans loaded via Google Fonts link in index.html
- Always: Show loading state with descriptive message during every API call
- Always: Strip ```json fences before JSON.parse on every API response
- Always: Wrap all API calls in try/catch with user-facing error messages
- Never: Add auth, database, sessions, or any form of persistence
- Never: Add features not in this spec — park them in a comment marked // v2
- Never: Change the ROI formula
- Never: Change the system prompt text — copy from REFERENCE_prototype.jsx verbatim

